Severity : Medium

Priority : Medium

Description : User is redirected to Job search page, but the filters from previous search as still functional.

Steps to Reproduce : 
1. Open https://www.mcdonalds.com/de/de-de.html

2. Scroll to the bottom of the page (Home Page)

3. Press on Careers (Karriere) link
  Alternatively: Open https://karriere.mcdonalds.de/ directly

4. Click on "MÃ¶glichkeiten im Restaurant" from the top of the page.
  Alternatively : Open https://karriere.mcdonalds.de/moeglichkeiten-im-restaurant/ directly.

5. Scroll down until "Alle Jobs im Restaurant" button is visible and click on it.
  Alternatively : Press the button when the bottom banner expands.

Expected Result : The "Alle Jobs im Restaurant" button redirect to the Job Offers page, where all the Restaurant Job oportunities are displayed

Actual Result : The button redirects to the page, bug all the filters from the previous job search are still fucntional and remain active.

